data.description: Welcome to 302 Atasi Drive in the desirable Arrowhead neighborhood! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers 1,873 square feet of living space with all-brick exterior. Highlights include a covered front porch, fenced backyard, and a patio for outdoor relaxation. Inside, you'll find hardwood floors, a gas fireplace, and a modern kitchen with granite countertops, a beautiful brick backsplash, and abundant cabinet space that provides both style, functionality, and effortless organization. The master suite is a true oasis, showcasing a generous walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom. Three additional spacious bedrooms provide ample space for family members or guests. The convenience of the second bathroom, featuring modern fixtures and finishes, adds to the appeal of this exceptional home. Located just minutes away from the popular Shoppes at Eastchase, you'll have easy access to a wealth of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Conveniently situated less than 1 mile from the interstate ensures that commuting and exploring the surrounding areas are a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property your own. Schedule a showing today!
